WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.134 --> 00:00:03.470
- LIFE IS ALL ABOUT
MAKING CHOICES,

00:00:03.470 --> 00:00:06.240
AND I HAD CHOSEN TO ATTEND
UPPER PENINSULA STATE,

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:09.209
BUT I WAS STARTING TO WONDER,
WOULD ANYBODY CHOOSE ME?

00:00:09.209 --> 00:00:12.045
- HEY, MADISON.
- OH, HEY, ELLIOT.

00:00:12.045 --> 00:00:14.181
- WHAT'S GOING ON?
- YOU REALLY LIKE FRUIT, HUH?

00:00:14.181 --> 00:00:16.517
- OH, YEAH, I GUESS I JUST
TAKE 'EM BACK TO MY ROOM

00:00:16.517 --> 00:00:17.684
FOR IN-BETWEEN MEAL SNACKS.

00:00:17.684 --> 00:00:19.319
THAT WAY, I NEVER
HAVE TO PAY FOR FOOD.

00:00:19.319 --> 00:00:20.821
- WOW, THAT'S REALLY SMART.

00:00:20.821 --> 00:00:23.223
- YEAH, I'M ON THE FLEX-450
SEMESTER MEAL PLAN,

00:00:23.223 --> 00:00:25.225
SO AS LONG AS I DON'T GO
OVER 17 MEALS A WEEK,

00:00:25.225 --> 00:00:26.393
I AM GOLDEN.

00:00:26.393 --> 00:00:28.395
- WHAT UP?
MIND IF I CUT?

00:00:28.395 --> 00:00:30.931
I'M JUST GETTING CHIPS
USING ALL POINTS.

00:00:30.931 --> 00:00:32.432
THE MEAL PLAN'S
KIND OF FOR SUCKERS.

00:00:32.432 --> 00:00:34.101
DID YOU KNOW
THE PENINSULA PIT'S

00:00:34.101 --> 00:00:35.869
TAKING POINTS
AT ALL THOSE RESTAURANTS NOW?

00:00:35.869 --> 00:00:37.271
- REALLY?
- I DON'T KNOW,

00:00:37.271 --> 00:00:39.106
WOULD YOU MAYBE WANT TO GO
CHECK IT OUT SOME FRIDAY NIGHT?

00:00:39.106 --> 00:00:40.607
- WHAT--WHAT TIME?

00:00:40.607 --> 00:00:43.977
- THAT'S THE BEAUTY OF POINTS,
WHENEVER WE WANT.

00:00:43.977 --> 00:00:45.445
- OKAY.

00:00:45.445 --> 00:00:48.382
- WELL,
I'LL SEE YOU THEN, RED.

00:00:50.117 --> 00:00:51.418
- YOU WERE SAYING SOMETHING.

00:00:51.418 --> 00:00:53.420
- I'LL SEE YOU LATER,
MADISON.

00:00:53.420 --> 00:00:57.925 line:0%
 
- ♪ TODAY I AM THANKFUL

00:00:57.925 --> 00:01:03.463 line:0%
 
♪ I PRAY TO BE THANKFUL
'CAUSE OF YOU ♪

00:01:03.463 --> 00:01:05.499 line:0%
 
- ♪ THANKFUL FOR EACH DAY

00:01:05.499 --> 00:01:08.068 line:0%
 
- ♪ GOD, 'CAUSE OF YOU ♪

00:01:09.970 --> 00:01:12.306 line:0%
 
- AND SO I STARTED
SPENDING POINTS,

00:01:12.306 --> 00:01:14.541 line:0%
 
HOPING TO RUN INTO THE GUY
WHO TOLD ME ABOUT THEM

00:01:14.541 --> 00:01:15.642 line:0%
 
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

00:01:15.642 --> 00:01:18.445 line:0%
 
LOGAN, IT'S SO FUNNY
SEEING YOU HERE.

00:01:18.445 --> 00:01:21.648
SO THIS HAMBURGER
IS 300 POINTS.

00:01:21.648 --> 00:01:23.283
HOW MUCH IS THAT IN DOLLARS?

00:01:23.283 --> 00:01:24.785
- $3.

00:01:24.785 --> 00:01:26.220
- WELL, HOW MUCH
DO THESE FRIES COST?

00:01:26.220 --> 00:01:28.322
- 175 POINTS, RED.

00:01:28.322 --> 00:01:30.724
- HOW MUCH IS THAT
IN DOLLARS?

00:01:30.724 --> 00:01:32.426
-$1.75.

00:01:32.426 --> 00:01:34.828
- HOW DO YOU KEEP IT ALL
STRAIGHT?

00:01:34.828 --> 00:01:37.731
- MAYBE IT'D BE EASIER
IF I SHOWED YOU.

00:01:37.731 --> 00:01:43.437
LET'S SAY THESE FRIES
WERE 111 POINTS.

00:01:43.437 --> 00:01:47.140
YOU JUST HAVE TO MOVE
THE DECIMAL POINT.

00:01:47.140 --> 00:01:49.009
YOU GET IT NOW?

00:01:49.009 --> 00:01:51.278
- ♪ I COULD NEVER
WALK ON WATER ♪

00:01:51.278 --> 00:01:53.413
♪ THE WAY YOU DID
AS THE BIBLE SAYS ♪

00:01:53.413 --> 00:01:55.015
- THIS IS GREAT, HUH?

00:01:55.015 --> 00:01:57.951
- YOU KNOW WHAT YOU SHOULD DO
IS THROW A PARTY.

00:01:57.951 --> 00:02:01.054
WE COULD GO TO THE DEER DELI,
MAYBE PICK UP SOME NACHO CHIPS,

00:02:01.054 --> 00:02:03.423
COLA, COUPLE MAGAZINES.

